title: Two Bedroom Overlooking the City! Come Tour with Us!
posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Nestled in the Larkspur hills at the base of Mount Tamalpais, Skylark Apartments offers residents the latest amenities, large floor plans, parking, fireplaces, and more all with some of best rustic, city and bay views Marin has to offer.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'Today', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'Pet Policy: $ 500 refundable pet deposit for one pet, $750 refundable deposit for 2 pets.', '$75 Monthly pet rent per dog.', '$75 Monthly pet rent per cat.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Please contact the Leasing Office for more Information.', 'Deposit:', '$800', 'Leasing options:', '3 months,6 months,12+ months', 'Application fee:', '$50 per applicant', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Water, Sewer & Garbage will be based on community usage//Billed based on occupants , Gas & Electricity will be billed based on usage through PG&E', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Based on community usage', 'Laundry:', 'Shared', 'Parking type:', 'Covered, Off-Street', 'Parking notes:', 'One assigned parking per household.', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior:', 'Balcony/patio', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Ceiling fans', 'Wiring:', 'Cable-ready, High-speed internet', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Shared pool, Fitness center, Clubhouse, WIFI Lounge , Outdoor Ping Pong Table, Package Kiosk', 'Security and Access:', 'Elevator in Select Buildings', 'Views:', 'City, Mountain', 'Additional features:', 'Hardwood floor, Sauna, Non-Smoking Property, Vaulted Ceiling * Select Apartment Homes, Quartz Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Offered by:', 'Skylark Apartments', '** Prices may vary and subject to change', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
